plt.figure(figsize=(14, 6))
sns.lineplot(data=e42_events, x='time', y='TotalSteps', hue='Date', marker='o', palette='viridis')

xticks_interval = 7
xticks_positions = list(range(0, len(e42_events), xticks_interval)) + [len(e42_events) - 1]
plt.xticks(xticks_positions, e42_events['time'].iloc[xticks_positions], rotation=45, ha='right')

yticks_interval = 10
min_steps = int(e42_events['TotalSteps'].min())
max_steps = int(e42_events['TotalSteps'].max())
yticks = range(min_steps, max_steps + yticks_interval, yticks_interval)
plt.yticks(yticks)

plt.title('Total Steps Over Time (from E42 events)')
plt.xlabel('Time of Day')
plt.ylabel('Total Steps')
plt.legend(title='Day', loc='upper left', bbox_to_anchor=(1, 1))
plt.tight_layout()
plt.show()

day23 = e42_events[e42_events['Day'] == 23]['TotalSteps'].to_numpy()
day24 = e42_events[e42_events['Day'] == 24]['TotalSteps'].to_numpy()

total_steps_day_23 = day23.max() - day23.min()
total_steps_day_24 = day24.max() - day24.min()

days = ['Day 23', 'Day 24']
total_steps = [total_steps_day_23, total_steps_day_24]

plt.bar(days, total_steps, color=['green', 'blue'])
plt.xlabel('Day')
plt.ylabel('Total Steps')
plt.title('Total Steps on Days 23 and 24')
for i, total_steps_value in enumerate(total_steps):
    plt.text(days[i], total_steps_value + 0.1, f'{int(total_steps_value)}', ha='center')

plt.show()


print("Total Steps taken by person on day 23-12-2017 in dataset timeframe is ", int(total_steps_day_23))
print("Total Steps taken by person on day 24-12-2017 in dataset timeframe is ", int(total_steps_day_24))
